    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the red onion has softened, add the <strong>basmati rice</strong> and <strong>spinach </strong>and give everything a good mix up</p><p>Pour in the<strong> stock </strong>and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to very low and cook, covered, for 10-12 min or until all the water has absorbed and the rice is cooked</p><p>Meanwhile, drain and rinse the <strong>black beans</strong></p><p>Peel and grate the <strong>carrot<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong></p>",
